---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="How ByteLite Works - Recursive Compression Technology" description="Discover ByteLite's patent-pending compression using bijective pairing & SDD encoding. Technical blueprint reveals 90% of our algorithm. See the math.">
  <main>
    <section class="hero-section">
      <h1>The Technology Behind ByteLite</h1>
      <p class="lead">ByteLite employs recursive bijective pairing and Segmented Domain Dictionaries to achieve mathematically-proven compression beyond traditional limits.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="pipeline-section">
      <h2>Compression Pipeline</h2>
      <div class="pipeline">
        <div class="stage">
          <div class="icon">📁</div>
          <div class="label">1TB Input</div>
        </div>
        <div class="arrow">→</div>
        <div class="stage">
          <div class="icon">🔄</div>
          <div class="label">8→16 bit</div>
        </div>
        <div class="arrow">→</div>
        <div class="stage">
          <div class="icon">🔄</div>
          <div class="label">16→32 bit</div>
        </div>
        <div class="arrow">→</div>
        <div class="stage">
          <div class="icon">🔄</div>
          <div class="label">32→64 bit</div>
        </div>
        <div class="arrow">→</div>
        <div class="stage">
          <div class="icon">📚</div>
          <div class="label">SDD</div>
        </div>
        <div class="arrow">→</div>
        <div class="stage final">
          <div class="icon">💎</div>
          <div class="label">18 Bytes</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="how-it-works">
      <h2>How It Works</h2>
      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step">
          <h3>1. Bijective Pairing</h3>
          <p>Mathematical functions that uniquely map data pairs into single values, ensuring perfect reversibility.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <h3>2. SDD Encoding</h3>
          <p>Six specialized dictionaries that together cover the entire 64-bit space through optimized pattern matching.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <h3>3. Recursive Rounds</h3>
          <p>Transform data through iterative cycles until reaching minimal representation (≤8 bytes + metadata).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <h3>4. Perfect Reversal</h3>
          <p>Every transformation is mathematically reversible, guaranteeing lossless reconstruction of original data.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="key-innovation">
      <h2>Key Innovation</h2>
      <p>Our 200KB engine transforms any data—text, binary, media—through iterative rounds until reaching minimal representation. Information isn't lost, it's transformed into hierarchical instructions for perfect reconstruction.</p>
      <p class="patent">Patent Pending No. 63/807,027</p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    color: white;
    background: #060813;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .hero-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0a0a 0%, #1a1a2e 100%);
    border-radius: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00D4FF 0%, #FF006E 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .pipeline-section {
    background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.05);
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .pipeline {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    overflow-x: auto;
    padding: 1rem 0;
  }

  .stage {
    text-align: center;
    flex: 0 0 auto;
  }

  .stage .icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .stage.final {
    color: #00D4FF;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .arrow {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: #00D4FF;
  }

  .steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .step {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .step h3 {
    color: #00D4FF;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .key-innovation {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.05);
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .patent {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    color: #00D4FF;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .pipeline {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .arrow {
      transform: rotate(90deg);
    }
  }
</style>
